        <Parent_String>marine bodies of water by biome [300387630], marine bodies of water [300387626], bodies of water (natural) [300266059], natural landscapes [300132294], landscapes (environments) [300008626], Settlements and Landscapes (hierarchy name) [300008346], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
